            <h2 id="owner-bio-title">A small business website service built by Jason.</h2>
            <p>My name is Jason, and I started Rose &amp; Paw Digital Designs to help small business owners get clean, practical websites without making the process feel complicated or expensive. I wanted to build a service that focuses on clear wording, useful design, and the basics that help customers understand and contact a business.</p>
            <p>I am based in Lethbridge, Alberta, and I am originally from Vancouver Island. That move gave me a strong appreciation for how important it is for small businesses to be easy to find, easy to understand, and easy to trust online.</p>
            <p>Rose &amp; Paw Digital Designs works with small businesses across Canada, including service businesses, home-based businesses, local shops, and owners who need a stronger online presence but do not want a large agency process.</p>
          </div>
